--------------------------------

Gestura AI may, at its sole discretion, offer separate commercial
licenses with different terms (including royalty‑free licenses) to
individuals or organizations that prefer not to be bound by the PPL‑3%
Share. Any such agreement must be in writing and will govern to the
extent of any conflict with this License.

8. Governance and PPL Ecosystem
-------------------------------

Gestura AI intends to align this License with the broader Prosocial
Public License (PPL) ecosystem and may participate in or reference a
