10. Termination
----------------

If You materially breach this License and fail to cure such breach
within thirty (30) days after receiving written notice from Gestura AI,
Your rights under this License automatically terminate. Upon
termination, You must cease all use and distribution of the Project,
but this does not affect rights You granted to others in compliance
with this License prior to termination.

